theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 14
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "<Incoming Transmission from Pulsar...>

Sorry to teleport you in amongst the aliens.

Just kidding. I might do it again.


Anyway,

From low-orbit geological scans, I have detected an alien structure below the surface, in the next canyon.

You'll have to get the tunnel opened up again, the aliens sealed it when you arrived.

Unfortunately they forgot that there's a button to unlock the doors in this canyon. Idiots.


There's an elevator in the other canyon that leads to the underground structure. Be warned that the power in the central structure is no longer active, so if you haven't used your torch now's a good time to learn how. Press 'f'. Simple as that.


Once you're down there, explore inside and find out as much as you can. We need any advantage we can get. 

I've noticed increased alien activity in the northern regions of Meridia. They might be close to discovering their ancient technology that they so desire.


There's a teleporter somewhere in the underground structure that I can extract you from.


Oh, and I may have left a present somewhere down there for you as well.



<End Transmission>"

