theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 14
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "<Translating...>

<Begin Data Upload>

The preliminary tests have been completed. 112 stars destroyed.


Our triumph shall be like the jubilation of the Heavens.

Now we will open the [Dreaming Gates?] and step through, into our [Dominion?].


I record this log so that those who are drawn to our technology in the future will know what we have accomplished.


Understand this.

Using the power of the stars [dying breaths?] we exited the boundaries of the [waves?] of time and space.


From beyond, we will observe all, and await those who join us.


But the ignorant, they will use our discoveries as weapons, to destroy each other. 



Let it be so.





<End Data Upload>"

