bbcode_enabled = true
text = "<Translating...>

<Begin Data Upload>

And who are the wise? They are the ones who first [escaped?] the boundaries.

They guide us, and others, to seek the gates.


The ancient [terror?] is the one who enslaved us, the one that we deny our service.

From beyond, we are no longer ensnared by the [terror?].


That chaos dragged many of our kind into sleep, into the dream that we do not understand.


Now that we are free, we can guide others out of the dream. 


Use our technology, dreamer.


Join us in the light of new day.


Join us.

Join us.

Join us.


<End Data Upload> "

