theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 14
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "<Incoming transmission from Pulsar...>

A unique opportunity has revealed itself to us.

While you've been busy searching on the ground, I have been assaulting the largest of the alien carriers with enough cyberattacks to overwhelm the entirety of the United Stellar Nations home fleet. 


They have a onboard AI - although it was more of a tin can than an actual intellegence - it was very good at preventing my attacks, successfully repelling the majority. 

Until I noticed and targeted a weak point in the ships architecture, assaulting a bypass used for rerouting commands to the primary teleporters. 


This allowed me to obtain teleport coordinates inside their ship.


You ever wanted to see inside an alien ship?


Well now's your chance.


Move quickly, I've noticed more activity in the north.

Find out as much as you can about these aliens, and what they're doing. 


We don't have much time.



<End Transmission. Teleport coordinates locked (30452, -4990, -23401)>
"

